The paper deals with matching profiles and querying databases, which are common topics in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and databases (cs.DB). The use of filters and matching values suggests a focus on machine learning and data mining (cs.LG), while the evaluation of top-k queries and gap queries suggests information retrieval (cs.IR) and software engineering (cs.SE) respectively.
